Two side rails--mounted on both right and left side (left side not shown in photo) allow for additional attachments of weaver sling mounts, lights, and other attachments. If you are used to seeing 1941-1944 Mosins including the Ismash models you will be impressed with this model. Weapon has matching #'s. Comes with bayonet, (not matching #). Includes strap, pouches, oil can. This is a true collector item that is a must have for the serious collector. You will notice the metal is not all chewed up from speed grinding to get it into combat quickly. Also the escutcheons are real steel, seated perfectly, even the screws are uniformly centered  in the escutcheons  for the strap. They are not cheap tin, or missing altogether. Rifle also has HEX receiver.                     PLEASE NO TEXTS! Email only! Enjoy!
